{% doc %}
  @prompt
    crie um arquivo liquid para eu personalizar o codigo, Create a new Shopify Liquid section called shotz-marquee. It should display an infinite auto-scrolling image strip that moves continuously from right to left using CSS animation (no JavaScript required). Requirements:
    Header: centered eyebrow text (small, uppercase, with a ⚡ icon before it) and a bold main heading below it. Both configurable in the customizer.
    Marquee track: a horizontal strip of image cards that scrolls infinitely left using @keyframes with transform: translateX(-50%). The cards must be duplicated in the HTML (render the blocks loop twice) to create a seamless loop. Cards should have width: 280px, height: 360px, border-radius: 16px, and overflow: hidden.
    Each card is a block with: an image picker and a label text field. The label appears as a colored bar pinned to the bottom of the card.
    Customizer settings: eyebrow text, heading, label bar color (color picker), and animation speed in seconds (range: 10–60s). Apply speed as inline style animation-duration on the track element.
    On hover, pause the animation (animation-play-state: paused). Include a preset with 5 default blocks., nao funcionou, os cards nao estao aparecendo 
{% enddoc %}
{%- comment -%}
  SHOTZ Marquee Section
  Infinite auto-scrolling image strip with CSS animation
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign eyebrow = section.settings.eyebrow
  assign heading = section.settings.heading
  assign label_color = section.settings.label_color
  assign animation_speed = section.settings.animation_speed
-%}

<div class="shotz-marquee section-{{ section.id }}-padding">
  <div class="page-width">
    {%- if eyebrow != blank or heading != blank -%}
      <div class="shotz-marquee__header">
        {%- if eyebrow != blank -%}
          <p class="shotz-marquee__eyebrow">
            <span class="shotz-marquee__icon">⚡</span>
            {{ eyebrow }}
          </p>
        {%- endif -%}
        {%- if heading != blank -%}
          <h2 class="shotz-marquee__heading h1">
            {{ heading }}
          </h2>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>

  <div class="shotz-marquee__wrapper">
    <div class="shotz-marquee__track" style="animation-duration: {{ animation_speed }}s;">
      {%- comment -%} First loop {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="shotz-marquee__card">
        {%- if section.settings.image_1 != blank -%}
          <div class="shotz-marquee__image">
            {{ section.settings.image_1 | image_url: width: 560 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy', widths: '280, 560', sizes: '280px' }}
          </div>
        {%- else -%}
          <div class="shotz-marquee__image shotz-marquee__placeholder">
            {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag: 'placeholder-svg' }}
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
        {%- if section.settings.label_1 != blank -%}
          <div class="shotz-marquee__label" style="background-color: {{ label_color }};">
            {{ section.settings.label_1 }}
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>

      <div class="shotz-marquee__card">
        {%- if section.settings.image_2 != blank -%}
